"gesetzt, jedoch werden technische und personenbezogene Daten wie die IP-"
"Adresse vom Client an den Server des Service-Providers übertragen, um die "
"Nutzung des Services zu ermöglichen."

#: inc/overrides/pro/presets/SendinbluePreset.php:1
msgid "https://www.sendinblue.com/legal/privacypolicy/"
msgstr "https://de.sendinblue.com/legal/privacypolicy/"

#: inc/overrides/pro/presets/SoundCloudPreset.php:1
msgid ""
"SoundCloud allows embedding content posted on soundcloud.com directly into "
"websites. The cookies are used to collect visited websites and detailed "
"statistics about the user behaviour. This data can be linked to the data of "
